pe":"icon","settings":{"icon":"ruler","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cart_5ff0d365-e7f6-4c0d-ba13-a1e6e1141341.svg","heading":"Add items to your cartÂ ","text":""}},"template--21364325515582__7e487794-266c-4ddf-960b-d92a7901192a-icon-2":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"ruler","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/shoppay.svg","heading":"Check out with Shop Pay","text":""}},"template--21364325515582__7e487794-266c-4ddf-960b-d92a7901192a-icon-3":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"ruler","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/pay_de0b8355-e782-45c8-b636-52ea2a8923a0.svg","heading":"Choose to pay in installments","text":""}}},"block_order":["template--21364325515582__7e487794-266c-4ddf-960b-d92a7901192a-icon-1","template--21364325515582__7e487794-266c-4ddf-960b-d92a7901192a-icon-2","template--21364325515582__7e487794-266c-4ddf-960b-d92a7901192a-icon-3"],"settings":{"text_alignment":"center","icon_position":"top","icon_size":"xlarge","heading_size":"large","mobile_swipe":false,"color_bg":"#ffffff","color_heading":"#171717","color_text":"#171717","disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":false}},"93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-1":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"What is the option to pay in installments on Shop Pay?","open":true,"content":"<p>When checking out with Shop Pay, you now have the option to pay now or later. Paying in installments on Shop Pay allows you to split your purchase amount into four equal, biweekly installment payments with 0% APR, or monthly installments with no hidden or late fees*.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-2":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Which payment methods are accepted if I use the option to pay in installments on Shop Pay?","open":false,"content":"<p>For non-interest bearing orders, debit and credit cards are accepted through Shop Pay. For interest bearing orders, you can only pay using a debit card.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-4":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Is there a limit to how much I can spend on a single Shop Pay Installments order?","open":false,"content":"<p>Yes, 17,500 USD is the order value limit that applies to purchases using Shop Pay Installments, including discounts, shipping, and taxes.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-5":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Are there late fees?","open":false,"content":"<p>No, there are no late fees if you miss a scheduled payment.<\/p>","page":""}},"875480fc-042b-49c3-893e-04b70b54befa":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"What if I make a return on a purchase made through installments with Shop Pay?","open":false,"content":"<p>To request a refund, please contact us. Using our return policy, we will advise if a return is possible. If a return is possible, then the we will advise how much the refunded amount will be. After your refund is processed, the refund amount will be applied to your original payment method within 3-10 business days and your balance will be updated.<\/p>","page":""}},"8e88213a-cf48-4580-91cd-e28aa1b209dd":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Where can I find more information about terms and payments?","open":false,"content":"<p>Check out the <a href=\"https:\/\/shoppay.affirm.com\/help\/s\/article\/about-sp\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shop Pay Help Center\">Shop Pay Help Center.<\/a><\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-1","template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-2","template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7e2-1854085a96e7-collapsible_tab-4","template--21364325515582__93ffcb23-2c8f-4cc5-a7